metadata.name: Ash's Coffee Table
metadata.description: This NFT includes a custom coffee table created by Austin Wood Co. Shipping to anywhere in the lower 48 USA included. Customer must pay for international shipping. Email: Austinwoodco@gmail.com to create your dream work of functional wood art. PFP epoxy inlay available for 0.5 eth. *Disclosure: table in picture doesn't represent the item you will receive, buyer will be airdropped an NFT representing their specific item. Please allow 90 days from purchase of this NFT to receive your item.
